	<div class="posts">
	<a name="109397054955162594"></a>
    
    <h2><font color="#000080"><!-- 2004-08-31 -->
    
    Just Ducky, Simply Ducky.  And You?
    
    </font></h2>
    
    
    <p>
	Well, it seems there is more slip-streaming at Blogger (they call it pushing out changes, I call it pooping in the punch-bowl) and I will have to figure out what this mucking up of my HTML is all about.  (See the previous post.)<br /><br />Meanwhile, there are some other oddities, but the main point is solved.  All blogs are operating and now there is just the ordinary noise to deal with.  Time for breakfast.  Later.<br />
    </p>
	<span class="byline">posted by orcmid
       at <a href="http://orcmid.com/BlunderDome/clueless/2004/08/just-ducky-simply-ducky-and-you.asp">8/31/2004 09:39:29 AM</a>,
